  <div data-sqsp-text-block-content><p>Would you rather see Rockstar remaster <em>Red Dead Redemption 2</em> for PS5 and Xbox Series, or give the <em>original</em> Red Dead the full next-gen treatment it deserves? Let’s hear it in the comments!</p></div>

  

  

